metadata.name: Tweeter files #1
metadata.description: 2500 outraged left-wing Jackasses for the Cancel Culture because, if you can’t beat em’, join em’. 🐴🗽🤡  A self righteous gang of keyboard warrior donkeys threatens the very fabric of society as they try to manipulate, control, and censor all of Equestria with their threatening Tweeter Files.  A satire collection that pokes fun at the ridiculousness of following the herd. Tweeter Files laugh at the political theatre of today, shed light on the controversy revolving around censorship, and are a fun expression of our lives today on social media.  The metaphor behind our collection is Cancel Culture is stupid… So, we are going to roll with it and embrace the “fud” in our tweets and community culture…  Counter Culture > Cancel Culture.  Sincerely,    Tweeter Files #1
